{"tid":1974060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「乘勝追擊」粗口大律師陳文慧遭母校民生書院大部分舊校友聯署聲討","createTime":"2020-04-15T15:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T15:59:35.000Z","uid":230104,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b80f58a23ec3887832a2369e79afbd21787ac0ec","tid":1974060,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RdBDin1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdBDin1.png&h=6af16653&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfoqHPK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcfoqHPK.png&h=982bb564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒襲警罪的控方大律師陳文慧，被揭發懷疑在facebook多番發表不當言論，包括公開評論區諾軒案發的行為、侮辱陳淑莊為「雞莊」，辱罵法官「衰過狗」及「人渣垃圾」等，律政司至今未有譴責或跟進。其母校港島民生書院及民生書院的一群舊生、學生和老師聯署，批評校友陳文慧的言論令人側目，要求她交代。<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒早前被控襲警，私人執業大律師陳文慧獲律政司受聘為主控官。《蘋果》早前報道，指一個疑似屬於陳文慧的fb賬戶發表大量「藍絲」言論，包括以「曱甴」形容示威者及以「雞莊」形容立法會議員陳淑莊。該賬戶亦曾侮辱法官是人渣垃圾及「衰過狗」，更曾公開評論區諾軒案發的行為。雖然其言論被指涉藐視法庭，但律政司至今未有跟進，亦沒有評論將來會否繼續聘用陳。<br />\n<br />\n超過350名民生書院和港島民生書院的校友、同學及老師在網上參與聯署，關注同學會永遠執委陳文慧的不當言論。聯署信指，陳以大律師以及律政司外判主控官之尊，自當深明法律專業包括不偏不倚、謹言慎行；身為民生書院畢業生，學校教導亦想必了然胸中，但她發表的激進言論惹人側目，與律師及同學會永遠執委的身份難以共存。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信表示，非常擔憂陳文慧是否被社會誤會，或是真誠地認為相關言論足為後學之楷模，期望陳就事件回應公眾，「以安後學與社會之心」。<br />\n<br />\n自從多間傳媒報道事件後，該個fb賬戶的大部份帖文已經消失，陳文慧至今沒有作出回應。"},{"pid":"468f6d165aed20255cfa454713bdc2affd83e5d8","tid":1974060,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"陳芷菁老公係陳文慧fb忠誠粉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f289ef25fcb03f570fad8612240092c8c27634d","tid":1974060,"uid":104684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"狙死條八婆藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢再做檢控官害死d手足"},{"pid":"88a29ec60392aa115a620bd939f71f7fcef0b60c","tid":1974060,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"民生書院好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5421f302b0efad5a71396d2f2ec416f4f719d44e","tid":1974060,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3097ef2dd145bee8b9da2827d6655c2ffb620f66","tid":1974060,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"學689同藍絲，全方位追擊"},{"pid":"fd48f6e7e2514c1450c71c65579cd8749f8af348","tid":1974060,"uid":154667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d2eaa35e8cb0bfbb0de224e3094006e5a3c70e","tid":1974060,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"條撚樣一定同陳嫣虹志同道合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54a0d5be0134409578e852c6b215699fb78f498","tid":1974060,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"藍雪寶間學校都係扮低調用拖字訣，等人淡忘，復課後都要繼續向佢地學校投訴"},{"pid":"b764bee77b2b98bc8bab79b05f5a6484cf21989b","tid":1974060,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">借個位先 召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgNRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=b5ad8a80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A部分請㩒入去呢度<br />\n記得睇埋啊，好撚緊要啊</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">【偽 &middot; 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版<br />\n召喚聯署師長文Q&amp;A就放喺度啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1981260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1981260</a></span></div>"}]}